&lt;h2>Key Learning Objectives&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="key-learning-objectives">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#key-learning-objectives" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>After completing this section, you will be able to:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>✅ Create and configure items in your product catalog&lt;/li>
&lt;li>✅ Manage inventory items with proper classifications&lt;/li>
&lt;li>✅ Edit existing items and update specifications&lt;/li>
&lt;li>✅ Work with different document types effectively&lt;/li>
&lt;li>✅ Maintain data integrity across all operations&lt;/li>
&lt;li>✅ Apply consistent naming conventions and organization&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2>Essential Skills Checklist&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="essential-skills-checklist">&lt;/span>
