&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2>Troubleshooting Quick Reference&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="troubleshooting-quick-reference">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#troubleshooting-quick-reference" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;strong>Cannot create items?&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Check user permissions with administrator&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Ensure required applets are installed and activated&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>EcomSync not available?&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Verify EcomSync applet is installed&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Check integration settings and credentials&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Items not appearing in transactions?&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Confirm item status is active&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Check if item type matches transaction requirements&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
